nodes.text: Score de Force is an interview of Kevin Kiner conducted by Scott Chernoff and published in Star Wars Insider 111. Kiner talks about the different themes he uses for the TV series Star Wars: The Clone Wars, and discusses his talks with George Lucas, as well as the cues he takes from John Williams' themes. The article was later reprinted in Star Wars Insider Special Edition 2013.
